data.description: Huge home in one of Metro Atlanta's desirable communities is a must see!  Much larger inside than it appears!! New Roof with Architectural Shingles installed in 2019!!  New updated lighting throughout! Enter the two story foyer and enjoy an open floorplan with hardwood floring throughout the main level, a formal dining room, open kitchen with granite countertops open to the family room with a fireplace to enjoy on cooler days. There is a large guest bedroom with a full bedroom on the main level. Upstairs offers a Loft for an office or sitting area, Massive Owner's Suite w/Double Vanities, Separate Tub/Shower, two additional secondary bedrooms with a shared charming bathroom. Unfinished third floor has additional room to grow to accomodate a bedroom and bathroom. The extrmely large finished basement offers two bedrooms, a large bathroom, a family room and a recreation room.  Enjoy having tea on the rocking chair front porch with ceiling fans or the oversized screened porch overlooking the  huge fenced backyard bug free! Fresh paint, new carpet and more!! Very Spacious floorplan!! Awesome Community!  Close to hospitals, shopping mall and highway I20. Can Close Quickly! Don't Miss Out On This Fantastic Home! Come view this beautiful home today!
